name: [JIUN] [HOST COMMUNITY] [DOC UPLOAD ACTIVATION] - DOC UPLOAD ACTIVATION CRM (2.2, 2.3, 2.6, 2.8)

parameters.query:
=SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';

select distinct l.id, 
l.registration_no,
l.status, 
l.created_at, 
concat(u.first_name,' ',u.last_name)as name, 
u.email,
u.uuid
from listings l 
left join users u on u.id = l.user_id
left join (select distinct listing_id, country, city_id from listing_location) ll on ll.listing_id = l.id
where 1=1
and ll.country = 'Malaysia'
and l.deleted_at is null
and l.status not in ('approved')
--and l.id = '20035'
and l.created_at::timestamp between (NOW() - interval'10 minutes') and NOW()

parameters.content: ## Prep for first booking (After listings approved) 2.3 (WA)

parameters.query:
=SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';

select distinct l.id, 
l.registration_no,
l.status, 
l.created_at, 
concat(u.first_name,' ',u.last_name)as name, 
u.email,
u.uuid
from listings l 
left join users u on u.id = l.user_id
left join (select distinct listing_id, country, city_id from listing_location) ll on ll.listing_id = l.id
where 1=1
and ll.country = 'Malaysia'
and l.deleted_at is null
and l.status in ('approved')
--and l.id = '20035'
and l.created_at::timestamp between (NOW() - interval'3 months') and NOW() 
and l.approved_at::timestamp between (NOW() - interval'5 minutes') and NOW()

=SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';

select distinct l.id, 
l.registration_no,
l.status, 
l.created_at, 
l.updated_at,
ceil((EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM NOW()::timestamp) - EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM l.updated_at::timestamp))/86400::integer) as day_since_rejected,
concat(u.first_name,' ',u.last_name)as name, 
u.email,
u.uuid
from listings l 
left join users u on u.id = l.user_id
left join (select distinct listing_id, country, city_id from listing_location) ll on ll.listing_id = l.id
where 1=1
and ll.country = 'Malaysia'
and l.deleted_at is null
and l.status in ('rejected')
group by 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9
having ceil((EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM NOW()::timestamp) - EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM l.updated_at::timestamp))/86400::integer) = '3' or 
ceil((EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM NOW()::timestamp) - EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM l.updated_at::timestamp))/86400::integer) = '30'

=SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';

with first_listing as
(select distinct l.user_id, 
l.registration_no,
l.status, 
l.created_at,
l.first_approved_at,
concat(u.first_name,' ',u.last_name)as name, 
u.email,
u.uuid, 
ceiling((extract(EPOCH from NOW()) - extract(EPOCH from l.first_approved_at))/86400) as days_since_approved,
RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY l.user_id ORDER BY l.first_approved_at) AS rank
from listings l 
left join users u on u.id = l.user_id
left join (select distinct listing_id, country, city_id from listing_location) ll on ll.listing_id = l.id
where 1=1
--and l.status = 'approved'
--and l.deleted_at is null
and ll.country = 'Malaysia')
--
select * 
from first_listing fl
where 1=1 
and fl.rank = '1'
and fl.days_since_approved = '3'
--and fl.user_id in ('29759')

parameters.content: ## Invite to host comm whatsapp (3-days after first listing approved) 2.8

parameters.query:
=SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';

select distinct l.id, 
l.registration_no,
l.status, 
l.created_at, 
l.approved_at,
concat(u.first_name,' ',u.last_name)as name, 
u.email,
u.uuid,
(extract(EPOCH from NOW()) - extract(EPOCH from l.first_approved_at))/86400 as days_since_approved
from listings l 
left join users u on u.id = l.user_id
left join (select distinct listing_id, country, city_id from listing_location) ll on ll.listing_id = l.id
where 1=1
and ll.country = 'Malaysia'
and l.deleted_at is null
and l.status in ('approved')
--and l.id = '20035'
and l.created_at::timestamp between (NOW() - interval'3 months') and NOW()
and l.approved_at::timestamp between (NOW() - interval'3 day') and NOW()
group by 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8
having ((extract(EPOCH from NOW()) - extract(EPOCH from l.first_approved_at))/86400) between '1' and '2'
